edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline

Class JSONAnnotationReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.pipeline.JSONAnnotationReader

  • public class JSONAnnotationReader
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads annotations output put by JSONOutputter As JSONOutputter is not lossless, this reader will only read what is saved. TODO: Also need to read dependency parses and sentiment For more strict serialization, see AnnotationSerializer; e.g., ProtobufAnnotationSerializer.
    Author:
    *Angel Chang
